Palatka Water Works, a Corporation, Plaintiff in Error, v. City of Palatka, a Municipal Corporation, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Putnam; ■ Axtell & Rinehart, for Plaintiff in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.

No appearance for Defendant in Error.
